Package: ICD10AnalysisToolbox
Title: ICD10AnalysisToolbox: Convert Tabular ICD-10 Data into Incidence and Prevalence and Run Follow-Up Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Markus", "Ingold", , "markus.ingold@unimedizin-mainz.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to group provided ICD-10 data into incidence (time to event) and prevalence according to Phecode or CCSR convention. Using the included analysis and plotting function, the capacity of a variable to distinguish prevalence and incidence of illnesses across organ systems.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Imports: 
	dplyr,
	PheWAS
Encoding: UTF-8
